comment: When will the new season start I’m going crazy 😱😱😱

It's so good to see you back, Mary. I'm so sorry about your heart issues. I had tachycardia up until my cardiac ablation (best procedure I ever had...fixed it 100%), so I can empathize with you. It's scary when the resting heart rate gets extremely high and it'll make you feel soooo tired after the end of an episode. I hope you continue to make a speedy recovery. Sending positive vibes your way from Florida.
I'm glad you're doing better Mary❤.
